{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2295943, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自己长着眼睛去看，自己长着脑子去想", "timestamp": 1629169380, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295944, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自己去查史料啊，有独立思考没错，但侵华战争还有得洗？", "timestamp": 1629169386, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295956, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295944, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我就想问在哪能查到完全中立的描述，我只能查到中国人写的，显然无法做到中立", "timestamp": 1629169559, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295958, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "九十岁老人说多不多说少也不少，你要真想知道详细的就花心思找几个亲历者去问", "timestamp": 1629169578, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295965, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在树洞问这个问题是徒劳的", "timestamp": 1629169678, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295967, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295958, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 如何保证他们说的是真的，日本也可以有老将说“我们这是圣战”，总有一方在扭曲事实", "timestamp": 1629169683, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295975, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说白了我就想知道在哪能看到既非中国也非日本的历史记录", "timestamp": 1629169733, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295977, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295967, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以你认为真相和事实是什么？", "timestamp": 1629169748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295982, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "爱信不信呗，不信又不想去查，能拿你怎么办？", "timestamp": 1629169812, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295983, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295977, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我不知道啊，我学过的和能查到的都是当局者的描述", "timestamp": 1629169844, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295990, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295982, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我查了，真的没查到其他国家的描述，所以你告诉我在哪查", "timestamp": 1629169878, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295998, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295975, "tag": null, "text": "自己要有基本的事实判断，脑子是个好东西，可惜某些人只看形式。", "timestamp": 1629169902, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296000, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295975, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你就去找不是第三方的外国人的记录，日记啊回忆录啊新闻报道啊，不是中国人也不是日本人的那种\n当然你要说那也是自带立场那没辙，自己想办法穿越吧", "timestamp": 1629169907, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296003, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295990, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 类比德国是否恰当", "timestamp": 1629169920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这方面的日本学者研究也不少吧", "timestamp": 1629169932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296007, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当局的就都是错的？自己不会学着判断？", "timestamp": 1629169940, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这问题无解，你不信中国的言论，查到了外国史料，你也会认为带有同盟国/轴心国的立场偏见。如果你信后者不信前者，那说明你只是不信中国言论，那更无解了，侵华战争最大的受害者就是中国。你从出发点就是不信，不在于你是否找到了史料。", "timestamp": 1629170060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296018, "tag": null, "text": "这下子精小日井小🐸合体了", "timestamp": 1629170205, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296043, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你这陷入了历史虚无主义的怪圈了，因为照你这样的说法，一切历史都有可能是伪造的->一切历史都不值得相信，那就是没有历史", "timestamp": 1629170237, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296062, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢F和I，我明白了，这问题无解", "timestamp": 1629170392, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296062, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以我们只能接受一个不那么理想的解，那就是选择相信一部分东西，再以此为基础研究更多，去寻找规律，去作出质疑和判断", "timestamp": 1629170502, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296079, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296062, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有基本事实判断，不完全偏信，这还无解了🐸", "timestamp": 1629170578, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296118, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296079, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 希望你对一件事情不明白虚心请教的时候也有人这么高高在上的回复你", "timestamp": 1629170793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我懂你的感受，当读了一些历史，又读的不是很多的时候，都会陷入历史虚无主义怪圈，解决办法只能是读更多", "timestamp": 1629170846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296143, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296118, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这也太虚心了，然后无解了🐸", "timestamp": 1629171013, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296124, "tag": null, "text": "Re Jason: 谢谢，我还是读的少了", "timestamp": 1629171017, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296144, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz能发出这样的提问，说明已经很棒读的相对很多了，可以试试选修一些历史方面的课程，或者找一些相对专业的书看看，应该会有相对系统的方法教怎么甄别史料😂", "timestamp": 1629171199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296143, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 别跟他说，他不是来问问题的就是来听他自己想听的话的", "timestamp": 1629171207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296200, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2296172, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 确实 自己呆井里连基本的判断都没有，然后听别人说完还无解（", "timestamp": 1629171409, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296233, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有一套老照片丛书 叫西方的中国影像 里面不少外国人拍的侵华战争时期日军暴行 包括但不限于损坏文物 处决百姓和抵抗军 占领城市等等", "timestamp": 1629171660, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296240, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "家父在博物馆工作 因此之前也有机会亲眼见过这种老照片 如果洞主真的想了解的话 各地博物馆及民间收藏是很容易找到的", "timestamp": 1629171754, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "应该没什么史料比照片还有说服力了吧？", "timestamp": 1629171805, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2296282, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "口述史和回忆录也是很重要的资料 dz非得硬杠 只要中国人说的都不可信的话 外国人写的也有不少 比如拉贝日记 魏特琳日记啥的", "timestamp": 1629172182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2297164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295956, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 任何人的记忆都不可能是绝对中立的", "timestamp": 1629179109, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2299719, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 441024, "reply_to": 2295967, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: Wikipedia好一些", "timestamp": 1629204471, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 441024, "reply": 35, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "我就明着问吧，众所周知日本对侵华战争的描述与中国的描述完全不一样，他们不说那是侵略，编了一堆理由，那怎么判断哪一边说的是对的？\n如果我完全听信本国政府的，那假如我出生在日本，难道就理所应当的听信日本政府？", "timestamp": 1629169270, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629204468, "url": "", "vote": {}}}